00:42:46,457 --> 00:42:48,490
Why are you smiling?

796
00:42:48,492 --> 00:42:50,292
What do you mean?

797
00:42:50,294 --> 00:42:52,428
It doesn't bother you
that your friends,

798
00:42:52,430 --> 00:42:54,763
