800
00:42:56,400 --> 00:42:58,534
I said "bullshit artist."

801
00:42:58,536 --> 00:43:00,269
And what's the difference?

802
00:43:00,271 --> 00:43:02,538
'Cause I don't lie. Ever.

803
00:43:02,540 --> 00:43:04,707
