890
00:48:14,819 --> 00:48:16,618
Not my problem.

891
00:48:16,620 --> 00:48:18,021
I bet
there's not two Steinways

892
00:48:18,023 --> 00:48:19,688
in the whole state of Indiana.

893
00:48:19,690 --> 00:48:21,925
I guess you'd better move
your ass, then.

894
00:48:21,927 --> 00:48:23,962
Who you think you're
talking to, greaseball?

895
00:48:53,925 --> 00:48:55,657
<i>Dear Dolores:</i>

896
00:48:55,659 --> 00:48:57,726
<i>This morning
I had steak and eggs</i>

897
00:48:57,728 --> 00:48:58,995
<i>for breakfast.</i>

898
00:48:58,997 --> 00:49:02,999
<i>The band has been playing
at very ritzy joints.</i>

899
00:49:03,001 --> 00:49:05,301
<i>Dr. Shirley and I
are getting along pretty good.</i>

900
00:49:05,303 --> 00:49:08,037
<i>But sometimes
I think he gets sad,</i>

901
00:49:08,039 --> 00:49:10,605
<i>and that's why
he drinks too much.</i>

902
00:49:10,607 --> 00:49:14,010
<i>I never knew how very beautiful
this country was.</i>

903
00:49:14,012 --> 00:49:16,545
<i>Now that I'm seeing it, I know.</i>

904
00:49:16,547 --> 00:49:18,714
<i>You won't believe
how beautiful nature is.</i>

905
00:49:18,716 --> 00:49:21,017
<i>It is as beautiful as they say.</i>

906
00:49:21,019 --> 00:49:23,886
<i>And the traffic out here
