910
00:49:32,563 --> 00:49:33,795
<i>We are heading down south now.</i>

911
00:49:33,797 --> 00:49:37,100
<i>I will write you another letter
when we get down south.</i>

912
00:49:37,102 --> 00:49:39,836
<i>I love you. Your husband, Tony.</i>

913
00:49:39,838 --> 00:49:41,871
<i>P.S. Kiss the kids for me.</i>

914
00:49:50,781 --> 00:49:52,348
Got any family, Doc?

