You sit on a throne.

1646
01:32:18,396 --> 01:32:21,265
So yeah, my world is way more
blacker than yours.

1647
01:32:22,433 --> 01:32:24,300
Pull over.

1648
01:32:24,302 --> 01:32:25,467
What?

1649
01:32:25,469 --> 01:32:27,469
- Pull over.
- I ain't pulling over.

1650
01:32:27,471 --> 01:32:29,340
Stop the car, Tony!

1651
01:32:31,742 --> 01:32:33,242
What?

1652
01:32:33,244 --> 01:32:35,411
What are you doing?

1653
01:32:35,413 --> 01:32:37,248
Doc.

1654
01:32:39,216 --> 01:32:41,317
Doc, what the hell
