1655
01:32:41,319 --> 01:32:42,351
Doc.

1656
01:32:42,353 --> 01:32:44,253
Get back in the car.

1657
01:32:44,255 --> 01:32:47,091
Yes, I live in a castle, Tony!
Alone.

1658
01:32:49,260 --> 01:32:51,460
And rich white people pay me
to play piano for them

1659
01:32:51,462 --> 01:32:53,262
because it makes them
feel cultured.

1660
01:32:53,264 --> 01:32:55,731
But as soon as I step off
that stage, I go right back

1661
01:32:55,733 --> 01:32:58,200
to being just another nigger
to them.

1662
01:32:58,202 --> 01:33:00,235
Because that is
their true culture.

1663
01:33:00,237 --> 01:33:02,271
And I suffer that slight alone,

1664
01:33:02,273 --> 01:33:03,772
because I'm not accepted
by my own people

1665
01:33:03,774 --> 01:33:06,308
'cause I'm not like them,
either.

1666
01:33:06,310 --> 01:33:09,511
So, if I'm not black enough
and if I'm not white enough

1667
01:33:09,513 --> 01:33:13,351
