then tell me, Tony, what am I?

1668
01:33:47,284 --> 01:33:49,286
I need some sleep.

1669
01:33:52,423 --> 01:33:54,423
All right.

1670
01:33:54,425 --> 01:33:56,425
I'll stop at the next place
we see

1671
01:33:56,427 --> 01:33:57,693
and sneak you into my room.

1672
01:33:57,695 --> 01:33:59,461
No. No.

1673
01:33:59,463 --> 01:34:01,563
I refuse to stay
in an establishment

1674
01:34:01,565 --> 01:34:03,434
where I'm not welcome.

1675
01:34:05,503 --> 01:34:07,438
Yeah. Okay.

1676
01:34:25,456 --> 01:34:27,692
Tony, do you have
to smoke everywhere?

1677
01:34:30,028 --> 01:34:32,394
I didn't know it bothered you.

1678
01:34:32,396 --> 01:34:35,364
You should have told me.

1679
01:34:35,366 --> 01:34:37,635
All you gotta do
is say the word, Doc.

1680
01:34:50,048 --> 01:34:53,482
You do realize you'll be home
before that letter arrives.

1681
01:34:53,484 --> 01:34:55,051
Yeah, I know.

1682
01:34:55,053 --> 01:34:56,752
Just thought I'd bring it
with me.

1683
01:34:56,754 --> 01:34:59,321
Save on stamps.

1684
01:34:59,323 --> 01:35:00,824
All right.

1685
01:35:00,826 --> 01:35:03,294
Tony, give it here.
I'll fix it.

1686
01:35:04,328 --> 01:35:06,062
No offense, Doc,

1687
01:35:06,064 --> 01:35:09,233
but I think
I got the hang of it now.

1688
01:35:15,406 --> 01:35:17,339
"Dear Dolores:

1689
01:35:17,341 --> 01:35:20,544
"Sometimes you remind me
of a house.

1690
01:35:22,780 --> 01:35:26,448
"A house with
beautiful lights on it,

1691
01:35:26,450 --> 01:35:29,453
where everyone
is happy inside."

