Yes, Tony. You got it.

1693
01:35:36,828 --> 01:35:39,394
Yeah?

1694
01:35:40,698 --> 01:35:43,367
Thanks.

1695
01:35:44,903 --> 01:35:49,671
Hey, Doc, thanks for helping me
with, uh, the letters.

1696
01:35:49,673 --> 01:35:52,474
You're really good
at writing 'em.

1697
01:35:52,476 --> 01:35:54,645
My pleasure, Tony.

1698
01:35:55,814 --> 01:35:57,780
You know, um,
when you get home,

1699
01:35:57,782 --> 01:36:01,719
maybe you should write...
write one to your brother.

1700
01:36:03,721 --> 01:36:06,923
