1712
01:37:06,784 --> 01:37:08,519
Come on in.

1713
01:37:10,822 --> 01:37:13,859
All righty.

1714
01:37:15,693 --> 01:37:17,526
Welcome, Mr. Shirley.

1715
01:37:17,528 --> 01:37:19,628
