1717
01:37:20,899 --> 01:37:22,631
Thank you, Mr. Kindell.

1718
01:37:22,633 --> 01:37:24,000
This is Mr. Tony Vallelonga.

1719
01:37:24,002 --> 01:37:25,767
- Nice to meet you, Tony.
