1733
01:37:49,727 --> 01:37:51,060
Where's the restaurant?

1734
01:37:51,062 --> 01:37:52,996
Well, you continue
down the hall here, Tony,

1735
01:37:52,998 --> 01:37:54,998
to the right
and across the lobby.

1736
01:37:55,000 --> 01:37:57,534
