1745
01:38:44,950 --> 01:38:46,883
Oh.

1746
01:38:46,885 --> 01:38:49,118
Last show. Cold War over.

1747
01:38:49,120 --> 01:38:50,587
Time for truce.

1748
01:38:52,057 --> 01:38:54,057
